---
title: BBQ-Spiced Double Pork Chops with Roasted Vegetable Medley
description: Letting the oven do the work is key for a busy family! Tonight, after searing the pork, everything will roast away in the oven so that your hands are freed up! This is the easy way to put beautiful vegetables and succulent BBQ-spiced pork on the table for all to enjoy.
